Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Nuclear power
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z8m26
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 3 Aug 1975
Warnings over safeguarding nuclear power so it can not produce weapons. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.